rows.label: bf08150100_0010
rows.name:
I didn't know there were
monsters like that...

rows.label: bf08150100_0020
rows.name: Nothing like Alst, for sure.

rows.label: bf08150100_0030
rows.name: Their healing abilities are unnatural.

rows.label: bf08150100_0040
rows.name: Similar to what Blades can do.

rows.label: bf08150100_0050
rows.name:
Most likely... remnants from the
civilization that created Blades.

rows.label: bf08150100_0060
rows.name:
If this truly is God's world,
that would make sense.

rows.label: bf08150100_0070
rows.name: I wonder what God is really like...

rows.label: bf08150100_0080
rows.name: I've never actually met him.

rows.label: bf08150100_0090
rows.name:
I only have fragments of
memories Just an image of him.

rows.label: bf08150100_0100
rows.name: That's why I want to meet him.

rows.label: bf08150100_0110
rows.name:
He built such an amazing
civilization, right?

rows.label: bf08150100_0120
rows.name: Then surely he must be...

rows.label: bf08150100_0130
rows.name: Amazing? This?

rows.label: bf08150100_0140
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ]ï¼Ÿ

rows.label: bf08150100_0150
rows.name:
It's nothing but ruins.
Just look around you.

rows.label: bf08150100_0160
rows.name:
Everything melted down
by weapons of war.

rows.label: bf08150100_0170
rows.name:
Here lies... nothing but the
buried sins of humanity.

rows.label: bf08150100_0180
rows.name:
If it's said that God was born here,
Then sin, too, exists with God.

rows.label: bf08150100_0190
rows.name:
After all, they're the same
as you people from Alst...

rows.label: bf08150100_0200
rows.name: Why do you hate us so much?

rows.label: bf08150100_0210
rows.name: What is it that you think we've done?

rows.label: bf08150100_0220
rows.name: Shin!

rows.label: bf08150100_0230
rows.name: That...That's...

rows.label: bf08150100_0240
rows.name: Iira...
